    Content: Executive summary + details
    Tool: SendGrid API + PDF generator

  SMS Alert (Critical Issues):
    Format: Text message
    Timing: Immediate for critical issues
    Content: Brief issue description + link
    Tool: Twilio API

  Webhook Notification:
    Format: JSON payload
    Timing: Completion + any critical events
    Content: Structured data for integrations
    Tool: HTTP POST to client endpoint
```

